snippet.textDisplay:
Hello Everyone,

I thank all of you for listening this, who cannot understand the lyrics.

It's actually a naat (praise words for the World's Last Prophet (P.B.U.H)).

"Tu Kuja Mann Kuja" means "you are something else i am something else, like a common person can say to Bill Gates that with amazement. It implies that i can never be like you.

A little effort to explain.
